      <title>Cuomo就其对美国调查的回应就加密货币交易所提供了建议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/cuomo-advised-crypto-exchange-okx-on-its-response-to-us-probe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约市长候选人安德鲁·库莫（Andrew Cuomo）曾担任离岸加密货币交易所的有偿顾问，因为它处理了联邦调查，然后才承认在美国非法开展业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/cuomo-advised-crypto-exchange-okx-on-its-response-to-us-probe</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 19:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
